    <string name="mph_info_title">About km/h and mph</string>
    <string name="mph_info_message">
    SpeedAlert can convert both GPS speed and road speed limits.\n\n
    • If you drive in a km/h country but prefer mph, both values are converted.\n
    • If you drive in an mph country but prefer km/h, both values are converted.\n
    • If your preference matches the country, no conversion is done.\n\n
    This ensures the display always matches your chosen unit.
    </string>

